      • containsCharSequence

        public static <any> containsCharSequence(CharSequence substring)
        Creates a matcher that matches if the examined CharSequence contains the specified CharSequence anywhere.

        For example: 

        assertThat("myStringOfNote", containsCharSequence("ring"))
        Parameters:
        substring - the substring that the returned matcher will expect to find within any examined string
